{"body": "Anytime you run `bundle update X`, child dependencies of X are unlocked in the resolution step.\n\nIf you modify a dependency in the Gemfile and run `bundle install`, only the gems that you modified and dependencies of that gem that are not shared by other gems are unlocked.\n\nWhen you run `bundle update`, all gems are unlocked.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/6128996", "created_at": "2012-06-05T16:09:44Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/6610#issuecomment-6128996", "updated_at": "2012-06-05T16:09:44Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 6610, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/wycats/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/wycats/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/wycats/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/wycats", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/wycats/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/wycats", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/wycats/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/428167a3ec72235ba971162924492609?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Fa87ff679a2f3e71d9181a67b7542122c.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/wycats/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/wycats/received_events", "gravatar_id": "428167a3ec72235ba971162924492609", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/wycats/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "wycats", "type": "User", "id": 4, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/wycats/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "52380636bd3543c15100c8ac"}, "id": 6128996, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/6610"}
